session50-create hybrid framework
---------------------------------

Loggin - record all the events in the form of text

Log Levels - All < Trace < Debug < Info < Warn < Error < Fatal < Off

Appenders - where to generate the logs (Console or File)
Loggers - what type of logs to generate (All < Trace < Debug < Info < Warn < Error < Fatal < Off)

import org.apache.logging.log4j.LogManager;  //Log4j
import org.apache.logging.log4j.Logger;  //Log4j
